tutorial.title: Unique Shadow Abilities
tutorial.content:
Shadows have different weaknesses and resistances than normal.
1. At the start of battle, 3 Shadows will appear.
When 3 Shadows have been defeated, the Warriors will leave and Valkyrie will appear.
2. When a Shadow is defeated, Valkyrie will receive a buff, and 1 more of the same Shadow will reappear.
3. If Setanta is defeated, Valkyrie receives the following effect: At the end of the turn, restores 20% of HP.
Stacks up to 3 times.
4. If Cu Chulainn is defeated, Valkyrie receives the following effect: When using a skill, all Phantom Thieves are inflicted with <color=#FF423F>Army of Ruin</color>.
Army of Ruin: After acting, take damage equal to 30% of HP.
Stacks up to 3 times.
5. If Narcissus is defeated, Valkyrie receives the following effect: When using a skill, it performs a follow-up attack on the Phantom Thief with the lowest HP. Stacks up to 3 times.

Shadows have different weaknesses and resistances than normal.

When 3 Shadows have been defeated, the Shadows will leave and Valkyrie will appear.
2. When a Shadow is defeated, Valkyrie will receive a buff, and 1 more of the same Shadow will reappear.
